    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated rod bearings and throttle body actuators, addressing common platform weak points. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains tight with EDC (Electronic Damper Control) providing versatile damping profiles. Finished in Interlagos Blue, the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-driven enthusiast vehicle. A solid driver\u2019s car for those who prioritize mechanical integrity and visceral feedback.",
